author: Greg Walters, Michael Learmonth
title: The White House Now Wants Everyone Who's Visited New York City to Self-Quarantine
description: Roughly 1 in 1,000 people in and around the city are infected with the coronavirus, White House officials said, warning that those who leave the city risk seeding the infection in new places.
content:
WASHINGTON The White House warned that anyone leaving New York City should self-quarantine for 14 days, in the latest attempt to limit the spread of the novel coronavirus from the city thats become the epicenter of the outbreak in the United States.
